  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Part time Cashier",
  "description": "<p><strong>Roles & Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Process all sales transactions and handle cash, credit and all other forms of payments accurately and efficiently using POS (Point-Of-Sales) System</li><li>Responsible for cash collections, withdrawals and reconciliation of all transactions at the end of each shift</li><li>Maintain adequate stock levels of inventory such as receipt rolls and STEB bags</li><li>Perform daily housekeeping duties to maintain cleanliness and safety of work environment</li><li>Stay informed and adhere to duty-free allowances, age restrictions, and other relevant regulations</li><li>Engage with customers to encourage additional purchases to drive sales</li><li>Be the company’s front-line ambassador to uphold company’s branding and image</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Cashiering experience in FMCG industry will be an added advantage</li><li>Strong communication skills and able to work well within a team</li><li>Maintain a positive attitude and focus on customer satisfaction in a fast-paced environment</li><li>Multilingual skills will be an added advantage to assist international travelers</li><li>Ability to stand for extended periods</li><li>Able to commit to rotating shift hours, including weekends and public holidays</li></ul>",
